{
  "stem": "20710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we used to climb in there and sleep through the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then early in the morning, come out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this was going on [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] till let's see, this was '41, practically all winter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then, and it was-- was a very hard life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Just not much to eat, not much to-- and cold, and this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and then [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] towards spring, they start taking-- they start taking us again to-- to forced labor, to take us again, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So by-- by that time, they had already a concentration camp formed very close to our, to-- to Hanaczow, that the neighbors Kurowice.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they had only man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No-- no woman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that time, they started taking us, this was towards spring.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're taking us to this camp in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to go-- it was about at least seven miles, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to walk there, and work a whole day on the fields.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had to start preparing like for spring, you know, for planting and things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the evening to go home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was going on the whole summer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they didn't have facilities that time for woman, so they just had men who they used to take out on the-- on the roads to make, you know-- what would I say?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You know, the road that was going from there to Lwow, the main, and, you know, to-- you know, knock [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] stones into, you know, gravel and things, and make the roads.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
